title: Backstage...Where All Of It Is Rigged!

description:
The Breakfast Club brings you their behind-the-scenes interviews from the huge show out in Boston featuring Fat Joe/Remy Ma, 50 Cent, Fetty Wap, Fabolous & more! Plus Donkey of the Day goes to Ayesha Curry for accusing the NBA of being rigged! Her husband does play for the NBA, no? 73-9?
